### ðŸ·ï¸ Auto Tagger (scripts/auto_tagger.py)
Automatically tags photos using AI-powered object detection:
- ðŸ¤– Uses YOLOv11 for object detection and classification
- ðŸŽ¯ Adds Finder tags based on detected content
- ðŸ“ Perfect for organizing photos by content

### ðŸ” Blur Detector (scripts/blur_detector.py)
Identifies and separates blurry photos:
- ðŸ“Š Uses Laplacian variance to detect image blur
- ðŸ“‚ Moves blurry photos to a separate folder
- âœ¨ Helps maintain photo collection quality

### ðŸ“± Screenshot Detector (scripts/screenshot_detector.py)
Identifies and organizes screenshots:
- ðŸ¤– Uses AI and traditional CV methods
- ðŸ” Detects UI elements and screen contents
- ðŸ“‚ Separates screenshots from regular photos

### ðŸ”§ Utility Scripts
- **ðŸ“… move.sh**: Organizes photos into YYYYMM folders
- **âœï¸ renamer.sh**: Renames photos using EXIF date/time
- **ðŸ“± screenshot.sh**: Quick screenshot organization

